%H A029351 <a href="/index/Rec#order_29">Index entries for linear recurrences with constant coefficients</a>, signature (0,0,0,1,0,1,1,0,0,-1,-1,1,-1,0,0,-1,1,-1,-1,0,0,1,1,0,1,0,0,0,-1).
%F A029351 a(n) = floor((n+37)*(n^2+17*n+245)/12096 - (n mod 2)*(n^2+29*n+298)/576 + (((n+1) mod 3) - (n mod 3))*n/216 + (((n+3) mod 4) - ((n+1) mod 4))*n/192 + (((n+4) mod 6) + ((n+3) mod 6) - ((n+1) mod 6) - (n mod 6))*n/432 + ((n^3+5*n^2+6*n+2) mod 7)/7). - _Hoang Xuan Thanh_, May 10 2026
